        "habilidades_faccion1": "Void Portals",
        "coste": 10,
        "descripcion_escaramuza": "Once per turn, during the activation of an allied unit, it may spend 1 action to swap its position with another allied Line, Elite, or Hero unit within 18\" or less. Neither unit may be locked in combat.",
